data.text: Uttarakhand Patwari Recruitment 2024 Notification will be out soon. In the last exam cycle, the Uttarakhand Public Service Commission (UKPSC) announced 391 vacancies for the post of Uttarakhand Patwari. Graduate candidates could apply for the recruitment and practice questions from Uttarakhand Patwari's previous year papers and Uttarakhand Patwari Mock Test. The selection process includes Written Exam, Physical Efficiency Test, and Physical Standards Test. The Uttarakhand Patwari salary for the finally appointed candidates will be in the pay scale of INR 29,200 - INR 92,300.
